title: Lost Mayan Temple Within The Asteroid Belt
info:
Drive down 55 miles of open road, walk through whispers of the wild and find spacecraft, take off into space and fly through fields of stardust, discover the lost mayan temple within the asteroid belt, go inside, kill monsters, take treasure, enjoy life!!! 
-----
Greetings Necta-Sceners! Today I present you my "almost" Solskogen release. Almost because my remote email was lost in space during the power outage at the party place. People liked the tune tho so I wanted to share it here! Enjoy!
